{"article_id":"rAz3WIM8FtojJmzl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON/BEIJING","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump said on Monday","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"he would meet Chinese President Xi Jinping next month","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"as the trade war between the world ' s two largest economies intensified ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"sending shivers through global markets .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"China announced earlier","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"it would impose higher tariffs on a range of U.S. goods ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"including frozen vegetables and liquefied natural gas , a move","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"that followed Washington ' s decision last week","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to hike its own levies on $ 200 billion in Chinese imports .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"The U.S. Trade Representative ' s office said later","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"it planned to hold a public hearing next month on the possibility","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"of imposing duties of up to 25 % on a further $ 300 billion worth of imports from China .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Cellphones and laptops would be included in that list","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"but pharmaceuticals would be excluded ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"the office said .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The prospect","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that the United States and China were spiraling into a no-holds-barred dispute","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that could derail the global economy","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"has rattled investors","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and led to a sharp selloff on equities markets in the past week .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"A gauge of global stocks shed a further 1.9 % on Monday , its biggest one-day drop in more than five months .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"China ' s yuan currency fell to its lowest level since December","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"and oil futures slumped .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"who has embraced protectionism as part of an \" America First \" agenda ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"he would talk to Xi at a G20 summit in late June .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"\" Maybe something will happen , \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Trump said in remarks at the White House .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"\" We ' re going to be meeting ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"as you know ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"at the G20 in Japan","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"and that ' ll be ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"I think ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"probably a very fruitful meeting . \"","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Speaking several hours later at a dinner gathering at the White House ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"it should be clear in \" three or four weeks \"","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"if a U.S. trade delegation ' s trip to Beijing two weeks ago was successful .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"\" I have a feeling","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"it ' s going to be very successful , \"","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"The Chinese government ' s top diplomat , State Councilor Wang Yi , said during a trip to Russia","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that China-U.S. talks were not a \" one-way street \"","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"and needed to be conducted on the basis of equality ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"according to China ' s Foreign Ministry .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"\" Both countries ' negotiating teams have the ability and wisdom","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"to resolve each other ' s reasonable demands ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"and in the end reach a mutually beneficial , win-win agreement , \"","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"The comment period on the planned new tranche of U.S. duties","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"- which covers 3,805 product categories -","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"is much shorter than in previous rounds","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and could potentially leave Trump in a position","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"to trigger those tariffs by the time","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he meets Xi .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"U.S. farmers are among those most hurt by the trade war ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"with soybean sales to China plummeting","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"and U.S. soybean futures hitting their lowest level in a decade .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Trump said on Monday","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"his administration was planning to provide about $ 15 billion","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"to help farmers","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"whose products might be targeted .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Farmers ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"who are a core political constituency for Trump ' s Republicans","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"heading into the 2020 presidential and congressional elections ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"are growing increasingly frustrated with the protracted trade talks and the failure","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"to reach an agreement .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" What that means for soybean growers is that we ' re losing , \"","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Davie Stephens , president of the American Soybean Association , said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump and China 's President Xi Jinping meet business leaders at the Great Hall of the People in Beijing , China , November 9 , 2017 .","depth":4},{"id":73,"text":"/Damir Sagolj/File Photo -","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"RC1E974F0B70","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"China said on Monday","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"it planned to set import tariffs","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"ranging from 5 % to 25 % on 5,140 U.S. products on a $ 60 billion target list .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"It said","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"the tariffs would take effect on June 1 .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"\" China ' s adjustment on additional tariffs is a response to U.S. unilateralism and protectionism , \"","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"its finance ministry said .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"\" China hopes","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"the U.S. will get back to the right track of bilateral trade and economic consultations","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"and meet with China halfway . \"","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"In the middle of the negotiations last week , Trump hiked tariffs on $ 200 billion of Chinese goods to 25 % from 10 % .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"The move affected 5,700 categories of Chinese products ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"including internet modems and routers .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Sources have said","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"talks stalled","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"after China tried to delete commitments from a draft agreement","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"that its laws would be changed","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"to enact new policies on issues from intellectual property protection to forced technology transfers .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"Beijing said on Monday","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"it would never surrender to external pressure .","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"Its state media kept up a steady drum beat of strongly worded commentary ,","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"reiterating","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that the door to talks was always open","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"but vowing","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that China would defend its national interests and dignity .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"State television said in a commentary","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"the effect of the U.S. tariffs on the Chinese economy was \" totally controllable . \"","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"Trump has said","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"he is in no rush to finalize a deal with China .","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"He again defended the move","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"to hike U.S. tariffs","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"there was no reason","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"why American consumers would pay the costs .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Economists and industry consultants , however , maintain","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"that it is U.S. businesses that will pay the costs","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"and likely pass them on to consumers .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"U.S. tariffs last year triggered retaliation by China ,","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"which imposed 25 % levies on $ 50 billion worth of U.S. products","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"including soybeans , beef and pork and lower tariffs on a list of $ 60 billion in goods .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"Goldman Sachs economists said in a research note","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"new evidence showed","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"the costs of Washington ' s tariffs on China last year had fallen entirely on U.S. businesses and households , with no clear reduction in prices","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"charged by Chinese exporters .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"They said","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"the effects of the tariffs had spilled over noticeably to the prices","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"charged by U.S. producers","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"competing with goods","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"affected by the levies .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":247,"left":195,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":125,"right":194,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":147,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":128,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":126,"right":127,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"